respect to 8 collective bargaining agreements covering most of our employees represented by the BCTGM. All of those
collective bargaining agreements expired in 2016. In 2018, we executed a complete withdrawal from the Fund and
recorded a $429 million estimated withdrawal liability. On July 11, 2019, we received an undiscounted withdrawal
liability assessment from the Fund totaling $526 million requiring pro-rata monthly payments over 20 years and we
recorded a $35 million final adjustment to reduce our withdrawal liability as of June 30, 2019. We
